title: [Hyacinthe's Outfitting]
description: Beneath a low skylight-set ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the white silk-paneled walls.  A long mistwood counter and some carved haon pegs sit in opposite corners while a woven Vornavian silk rug rests on an unfinished wooden floor.
